{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b0db9a90-95bc-4a01-b247-1ddb33e1a2a8",
    "name": "amvision yolox training api",
    "description": "当前公开的 YOLOX training create/list/detail/validation-metrics/train-metrics/output-files 接口。本集合已经同步 evaluation_interval、gpu_count、precision、latest checkpoint、validation metrics、output-files 和 training_summary 查询字段，可直接用于本机调试。",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "YOLOX Training",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create YOLOX Training Task",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 202) {",
                  "  var payload = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('taskId', payload.task_id);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('datasetExportId', payload.dataset_export_id);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('datasetExportManifestKey', payload.dataset_export_manifest_key);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('datasetVersionId', payload.dataset_version_id);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('formatId', payload.format_id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-principal-id",
                "value": "{{principalId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-project-ids",
                "value": "{{projectId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-scopes",
                "value": "datasets:read,tasks:write",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"project_id\": \"{{projectId}}\",\n  \"dataset_export_id\": \"{{datasetExportId}}\",\n  \"dataset_export_manifest_key\": null,\n  \"recipe_id\": \"{{recipeId}}\",\n  \"model_scale\": \"{{modelScale}}\",\n  \"output_model_name\": \"{{outputModelName}}\",\n  \"warm_start_model_version_id\": null,\n  \"evaluation_interval\": {{evaluationInterval}},\n  \"max_epochs\": {{maxEpochs}},\n  \"batch_size\": {{batchSize}},\n  \"gpu_count\": {{gpuCount}},\n  \"precision\": \"{{precision}}\",\n  \"input_size\": [{{inputWidth}}, {{inputHeight}}],\n  \"extra_options\": {\n    \"seed\": 42\n  },\n  \"display_name\": \"{{displayName}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/models/yolox/training-tasks",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "models",
                "yolox",
                "training-tasks"
              ]
            },
            "description": "以 DatasetExport 为唯一输入边界创建 YOLOX 训练任务。当前请求体已经同步 model_scale、evaluation_interval、gpu_count、precision、batch_size、max_epochs、input_size 和 warm_start_model_version_id；precision 字段可写 fp8、fp16、fp32，但当前最小真实训练执行器实际只支持 fp16、fp32。evaluation_interval 表示每隔多少轮执行一次真实验证评估，默认 5，最后一轮会强制补做一次评估，并回写 map50、map50_95。warm_start_model_version_id 表示本次训练要从哪个已有 ModelVersion 对应的 checkpoint 开始训练，而不是从随机初始化开始；来源既可以是当前 Project 自己已有的历史训练产出，也可以是平台基础模型目录中登记的 pretrained-reference ModelVersion。若需要选择平台基础模型来源，可先查询 /api/v1/models/platform-base 或 /api/v1/models/platform-base/{model_id}，再把 available_versions[].model_version_id 填入 warm_start_model_version_id。"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List YOLOX Training Tasks",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  var payload = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (Array.isArray(payload) && payload.length > 0) {",
                  "    var first = payload[0];",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('taskId', first.task_id);",
                  "    if (first.model_version_id) pm.collectionVariables.set('modelVersionId', first.model_version_id);",
                  "    if (first.output_object_prefix) pm.collectionVariables.set('outputObjectPrefix', first.output_object_prefix);",
                  "    if (first.checkpoint_object_key) pm.collectionVariables.set('checkpointObjectKey', first.checkpoint_object_key);",
                  "    if (first.latest_checkpoint_object_key) pm.collectionVariables.set('latestCheckpointObjectKey', first.latest_checkpoint_object_key);",
                  "    if (first.metrics_object_key) pm.collectionVariables.set('metricsObjectKey', first.metrics_object_key);",
                  "    if (first.validation_metrics_object_key) pm.collectionVariables.set('validationMetricsObjectKey', first.validation_metrics_object_key);",
                  "    if (first.summary_object_key) pm.collectionVariables.set('summaryObjectKey', first.summary_object_key);",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-principal-id",
                "value": "{{principalId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-project-ids",
                "value": "{{projectId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-scopes",
                "value": "tasks:read",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/models/yolox/training-tasks?project_id={{projectId}}&dataset_export_id={{datasetExportId}}&limit={{trainingLimit}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "models",
                "yolox",
                "training-tasks"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "project_id",
                  "value": "{{projectId}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "dataset_export_id",
                  "value": "{{datasetExportId}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "dataset_export_manifest_key",
                  "value": "{{datasetExportManifestKey}}",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "state",
                  "value": "{{trainingState}}",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "created_by",
                  "value": "{{createdBy}}",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "{{trainingLimit}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "按 DatasetExport 边界列出 YOLOX 训练任务。当前 collection 已预留 state、created_by、dataset_export_manifest_key 和 limit 查询参数，并会自动回填 model_version_id、训练输出文件路径等常用变量。running 阶段如果任务已经开始，还会直接返回 validation_metrics_object_key，便于定位中间验证快照。"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get YOLOX Training Task Detail",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  var payload = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (payload.model_version_id) pm.collectionVariables.set('modelVersionId', payload.model_version_id);",
                  "  if (payload.output_object_prefix) pm.collectionVariables.set('outputObjectPrefix', payload.output_object_prefix);",
                  "  if (payload.checkpoint_object_key) pm.collectionVariables.set('checkpointObjectKey', payload.checkpoint_object_key);",
                  "  if (payload.latest_checkpoint_object_key) pm.collectionVariables.set('latestCheckpointObjectKey', payload.latest_checkpoint_object_key);",
                  "  if (payload.metrics_object_key) pm.collectionVariables.set('metricsObjectKey', payload.metrics_object_key);",
                  "  if (payload.validation_metrics_object_key) pm.collectionVariables.set('validationMetricsObjectKey', payload.validation_metrics_object_key);",
                  "  if (payload.summary_object_key) pm.collectionVariables.set('summaryObjectKey', payload.summary_object_key);",
                  "}",
                  ""
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-principal-id",
                "value": "{{principalId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-project-ids",
                "value": "{{projectId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-scopes",
                "value": "tasks:read",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/models/yolox/training-tasks/{{taskId}}?include_events={{includeEvents}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "models",
                "yolox",
                "training-tasks",
                "{{taskId}}"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "include_events",
                  "value": "{{includeEvents}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "查询单条 YOLOX 训练任务详情和事件流。详情响应已经同步 output_object_prefix、latest_checkpoint_object_key、validation_metrics_object_key，以及 training_summary.output_files 和 validation 摘要。running 阶段的 task.progress 当前会带 validation_ran、evaluated_epochs，以及评估轮的 map50、map50_95。"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get YOLOX Training Validation Metrics",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-principal-id",
                "value": "{{principalId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-project-ids",
                "value": "{{projectId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-scopes",
                "value": "tasks:read",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/models/yolox/training-tasks/{{taskId}}/validation-metrics",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "models",
                "yolox",
                "training-tasks",
                "{{taskId}}",
                "validation-metrics"
              ]
            },
            "description": "直接通过 HTTP 返回当前训练任务最新的 validation-metrics.json 内容。当前响应统一为 file_status、task_state、object_key 和 payload；running 阶段只要已经执行过真实评估轮，这个接口就会返回 ready 和完整 payload；尚未生成验证文件时返回 pending 和空 payload。"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get YOLOX Training Train Metrics",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-principal-id",
                "value": "{{principalId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-project-ids",
                "value": "{{projectId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-scopes",
                "value": "tasks:read",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/models/yolox/training-tasks/{{taskId}}/train-metrics",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "models",
                "yolox",
                "training-tasks",
                "{{taskId}}",
                "train-metrics"
              ]
            },
            "description": "直接通过 HTTP 返回当前训练任务最新的 train-metrics.json 内容。当前响应统一为 file_status、task_state、object_key 和 payload；若训练指标文件尚未生成，接口会返回 pending 和空 payload；训练完成且文件已写出后，接口会返回 ready 和完整 payload。"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List YOLOX Training Output Files",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-principal-id",
                "value": "{{principalId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-project-ids",
                "value": "{{projectId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-scopes",
                "value": "tasks:read",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/models/yolox/training-tasks/{{taskId}}/output-files",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "models",
                "yolox",
                "training-tasks",
                "{{taskId}}",
                "output-files"
              ]
            },
            "description": "统一列出 train-metrics、validation-metrics、summary、labels、best-checkpoint、latest-checkpoint 这 6 个训练输出文件的读取状态。前端可以只轮询这个资源组，根据 file_status 判断每个文件是否已经 ready。"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get YOLOX Training Output File Detail",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-principal-id",
                "value": "{{principalId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-project-ids",
                "value": "{{projectId}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-amvision-scopes",
                "value": "tasks:read",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/models/yolox/training-tasks/{{taskId}}/output-files/{{outputFileName}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "models",
                "yolox",
                "training-tasks",
                "{{taskId}}",
                "output-files",
                "{{outputFileName}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "统一读取单个训练输出文件。summary、train-metrics、validation-metrics 会在 payload 中返回 JSON；labels 会在 text_content 和 lines 中返回文本；best-checkpoint、latest-checkpoint 当前只返回文件状态和元数据。"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
